ee561f38.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

d7ceae39.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

96f16a29.text: It's been years since I last saw her.
96f16a29.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

903e3445.text: My brother asked me to let her stay on my place since she's going to college.
903e3445.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

0b214ef7.text: He said she wanted to study here as the quality of education is good.
0b214ef7.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

d1359c8e.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

5840685c.text: My brother and I went to the same college.
5840685c.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

a48bf4ac.text: It was the best years of my life, academically speaking.
a48bf4ac.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

447e15a2.text: And the worst years of my life, socially speaking.
447e15a2.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

19ccd065.text: We took our own path after college.
19ccd065.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

e776ac97.text: I chose to pursue my career here in the city.
e776ac97.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

71b95a6e.text: My brother went back to our hometown where he built his family.
71b95a6e.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

003822ca.text: I think the main reason for me staying here is because of the opportunities.
003822ca.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

67730d11.text: The city is always the best option for good-paying jobs.
67730d11.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

7f4efe7d.text: I was working as a full-time programmer before.
7f4efe7d.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

eca6a2b6.text: Now I'm working as a freelance programmer.
eca6a2b6.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

c46dec56.text: As for my brother, he pursued farming to continue the legacy of our family.
c46dec56.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

8efe9f66.text: I guess it's kinda ironic how things went.
8efe9f66.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

408abba1.text: My brother lived his earlier life wild and adventurous while I lived mine as introverted and awkward.
408abba1.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

d3dca2ba.text: Now he's living a peaceful life in the rural areas while I'm trying to change mine.
d3dca2ba.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

8953716c.text: I'm trying to live the remaining of my life to the best of it.
8953716c.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

d8137260.text: I made a promise to myself that I will try to be not that kind of person that I was before.
d8137260.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

56ddb93b.text: It's still a long way but I'm on it.
56ddb93b.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

b765ad26.text: For a year, I've been hitting the gym.
b765ad26.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

f1176d2c.text: I think it was a great start.
f1176d2c.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

c8e5d9cb.text: Now I'm much more confident on how look.
c8e5d9cb.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

413a93e6.text: Especially that my niece is coming to stay.
413a93e6.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.

67511032.text: I think it's just right to be presentable right in front of her.
67511032.crowdinContext: A dialogue string by Main Character.
